；综合科组公开课；</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"115\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\" rowspan=\"2\">\r\n				<span> </span>\r\n				<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;\">教学处</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"440\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\" colspan=\"3\">\r\n				<span> </span>\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;\">以办公室为单位准备教师师德演讲赛</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"440\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\" colspan=\"3\">\r\n				<span> </span>\r\n				<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;\">周五至周日参加区中小学生田径运动会</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"115\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\r\n				<span> </span>\r\n				<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;\">体育科组</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>',2,'2013-11-17 23:57:58','2013-11-17 23:57:58',0,NULL,'0',13),(65,'作品','1',4,'2013-11-18 01:06:59','2013-11-18 01:06:59',0,'/assets/article/2013/11/18/zuop.gif','0',13),(66,'养成良好卫生习惯，共创美好校园环境','<span> </span>\r\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoPlainText\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>宋阳<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoPlainText\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>老师们、同学们：<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>大家早上好， <span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>今天讲话的主题是《养成良好卫生习惯，共创美好校园环境》<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\">校园是我们共同学习生活的地方，</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\">花园般的校园，到处绿树成荫，鸟语花香；宽敞的教室，雪白的墙壁，到处窗明几净，</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\">整齐摆放的桌椅，</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\">现代化的教学设施，这一切都为我们的学习、生活提供了更优越的条件、更优美的环境，优美的环境陶冶人生，优美的环境化育生命。</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\">我想在这样干净整洁优美的环境里，我们都会身心健康，学习进步。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;font-size:14pt;\"></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\" style=\"text-indent:28pt;\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\">这么好的环境来自哪里？这么好的环境自然来自我们的双手亲自去创造，共同维护。</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\">养成良好的卫生习惯，共创美好校园环境，是我们每个人的责任和义务。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\">首先我们应从自己做起，<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\" style=\"text-indent:28pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>我们应该时刻提醒自己，不要随地乱扔垃圾，不要随地吐痰。这些看似虽然无关紧要，但是造成的后果就是使我们的校园变得脏乱差。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\" style=\"text-indent:28pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>我们还要制止少数同学不讲卫生的行为，看到地上有果皮纸屑空瓶子要主动捡起来把它放进垃圾筒或者垃圾袋。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\" style=\"text-indent:28pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>另外我们每位同学都应该自觉地保护教室以及校园公共环境卫生<span>.</span>搞好班级和清洁包干区的卫生，做好保洁工作； <span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\" style=\"text-indent:28pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>我看到我们的同学早上进校门前把空的牛奶盒和早餐盒丢进校门外的垃圾筒；我看到我们的同学把清洁卫生工具整齐摆地放进各班的卫生工具保洁柜；我看到不少班级的课桌椅摆放的整整齐齐；我看到许多班级干干净净一尘不染；我看到不少同学的课桌上和抽屉里整齐干净；我看到上学期甘李的第一届同学集体到足球场拨杂草，捡石头；我还看到体育训练的同学携手把体育馆篮球场拖得干干净净；<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\" style=\"text-indent:28pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>一份耕耘一份收获，只要我们共同努力，坚持不懈，我们的校园就会像花园一样，令人精神振奋，令人追求向上。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\">让我们共同在飘扬的红旗下作出我们庄严的承诺：养成良好的卫生习惯，共创美好甘李校园。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><span>我的讲话结束，谢谢大家。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>',14,'2013-11-19 01:18:07','2013-11-19 01:18:07',0,NULL,'0',13),(67,'读书与人生','<span> </span>\r\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16pt;\">李秋艳</span><span style=\"font-size:16pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">老师们、同学们：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">大家早上好！很高兴能在这清新爽朗的秋日早晨和同学们谈谈读书这个永恒美好的话题。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">书，从我们出生开始，便对我们产生了影响。幼小的时候，我们从拼音表上牙牙学语；两三岁的时候，我们开始接受唐诗宋词的熏陶；童年中有多少个夜晚，我们在妈妈述说的格林和安徒生童话的奇幻世界中渐入梦乡。读书，伴随着我们走过童年时光，是书籍让我们的童年生活更加奇妙，更加富有诗意，更加丰富多彩。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">书，并不只是我们童年的伙伴，也是我们现在的知心朋友。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">闻一多先生说过；“一个人可以无师自通，但不可以无书自通。”在生活学习中遇到百思不得其解的问题时，我们应该把目光转向身边的书籍，在书中一定可以找到满意的答案。从法布尔的《昆虫记》中，我们可以了解螳螂这种瘦弱的昆虫为什么能捕杀比自己大得多的蝉这个自然界的秘密；从笛福的《鲁宾逊漂流记》中，我们可以感受到孤独也是人生的财富、孤独也可以激发人的创造；从高尔基的《童年》中，我还可以明白童年中的苦难是上帝送给人类的另一份礼物，它让我们在磨难中学会辨别真善假恶的道理。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">同学们，鸟语高飞先展翅，人求上进先读书。在读书的过程中，我们攀上了一级又一级新台阶；在读书的过程中，我们品味了千百种不同的人生；在读书的过程中，我们超越了一个又一个自我；在读书的过程中，我们渡过一个又一个的迷津。只要求上进，我们就应该无休止地读书。我们的人生少不了读书，我们的人生中不能不读书，我们的人生与读书不可分割。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">最后，希望同学们在读书节和今后的日子里徜徉书海，与好书为友，希望读书节，在你的心中，永不落幕！ <span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">我的演讲完毕，谢谢大家！<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>',14,'2013-11-19 01:19:23','2013-11-19 01:19:23',0,NULL,'0',13),(68,'甘李学校第二届读书节活动方案','<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">为了营造浓郁的读书氛围，引导和鼓励同学们走近书的海洋，养成多读书、读好书的良好习惯，进一步丰富校园文化生活，建设书香校园，</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">我校将举行第二届读书节活动，活动内容包括“征文比赛”、“剪报展示”、“手抄报展示”、“课本剧表演”、“汉字听写大赛”等，具体安排如下：</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.65pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-28.5pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>一、<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">活动负责：语文科组及班主任，主要负责人：中学部李秋艳，小学部祖光伟。</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-28.5pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>二、<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">活动安排：</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-36pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>1、<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:12pt;\">征文比赛（七、八年级学生参加）<span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-71.55pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">内</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">容</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">：我和书的故事</span><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">要</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">求：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）内容必须是自己的亲身感受，诉说你和书之间那些触动心灵的感</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-41.05pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">人故事，反映书在你成长道路上所起到的重要作用以及你收获到的关于“读书”</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-41.05pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">的一些感悟等。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-41.2pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）表达自己的真实情感和思想。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-41.05pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）认真审题，题目自拟，体裁不限。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）七年级：</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">字以上。八年级：</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">字以上。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-41.05pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）现场统一公布题目，在规定时间内完成。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;</span><b><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:12pt;\">时<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>间</span></b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:12pt;\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">日第七节班会课，由班主任负责监督学生完成，并将学生文章收齐交给语文老师。</span><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.85pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">奖项设置</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">：佳作奖每班</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">人、优秀奖每班</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">人</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.95pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">奖项评定：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">各班语文老师推荐</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">篇候选文章（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">日下午交给李秋艳老师），所有语文老师给侯选文章打分，依据综合得分确定奖项结果，时间统一在</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">日（星期三）下午第六节。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:12pt;\">、剪报展示（所有学生参加）<span></span></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">内</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">容：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">学生根据自己的喜好，选择剪报内容。</span><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">要</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">求</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">：（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）语文老师和班主任要指导学生搜集和整理剪报资料，要求学生提早准备，并以此促进学生“阅读和积累”的习惯培养。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）每个学生的剪报作品由自己独立完成，并注明班级、姓名。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）初中学生的作品要求注明搜集资料的时间，并穿插一些自己对所搜集资料和信息的简短评价或感想。</span><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">展示时间</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">—</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">日（第十一周一周），要求各班在</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">日下午放学前布置好。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">地</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">点</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">：各班教室门口走廊、墙壁。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">奖项设置</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">：每班设优秀作品奖</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">名，由班主任组织本班学生评定，并在</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">日前上报，小学部上报到祖光伟老师处，中学部上报到李秋艳老师处。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">摄</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">影</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">廖碧丹</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><b>3</b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">、手抄报展示（三、四年级和七、八年级学生参加）</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">内</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">容：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">学生根据自己的喜好，选择手抄报内容。</span><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">要</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">求</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">：（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）语文老师、美术老师和班主任指导学生制作手抄报。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）作品要注明班级、姓名，可以多人合作，但每份作品最多只能三人署名。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）每份手抄报要呈现一个主题。</span><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">展示时间</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">—</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">日（第十四周一周），要求各班在</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">日下午放学前布置好。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">地</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">点</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">：各班教室门口走廊、墙壁。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">奖项设置</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">：每班设优秀作品奖</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">名，由班主任组织本班学生评定，并在</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">日前上报，小学部上报到祖光伟老师处，中学部上报到李秋艳老师处。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">摄</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">影</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">廖碧丹</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><b>4</b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">、课本剧表演（小学各年级）</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">内</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">容：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">学生熟知的童话故事</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><b><span>&nbsp;</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">要</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">求：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）以熟知的童话故事或文学作品为题材，学生可以大胆想象，尽情演绎。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）以老师为单位，一位老师所教班级出一个节目。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）舞台背景、道具以简练、明快为原则，不宜过于复杂。（所用道具请自行准备）。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">）每个节目时间控制在</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">分钟之内。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">展示时间：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">日（第</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">周周五下午）</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><b><span>&nbsp;</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">地</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">点：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">体育馆</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp; </span><b><span>&nbsp;</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">奖项设置：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">以节目为单位，一等奖</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">名，二等奖</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">名，三等奖</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">名。最佳表演奖若干名。</span><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">奖项评定：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">小学部除语文老师外的所有老师担任评委，评选出</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">等奖的节目。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">每班选出最佳表演奖获得者一名，由每班语文老师选出！评选结果在表演结束后交给祖光伟老师。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">摄</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">影：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">廖碧丹</span><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;</span>5</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">、汉字听写大赛（方案待定）</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-28.5pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>三、<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">颁奖闭幕（全校学生及老师参加）</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">时</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">间：</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（星期一）早晨升旗仪式后</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span>',13,'2013-11-19 01:21:05','2013-11-19 01:21:05',0,NULL,'0',13);
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `articles` ENABLE KEYS */;
UNLOCK TABLES;

